verses.verse: Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> <S%H4427>reigneth<s%>; He is <S%H3847>clothed<s%> with <S%H1348>majesty<s%>; <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is <S%H3847>clothed<s%> with <S%H5797>strength<s%>; he hath <S%H247>girded<s%> himself <S%H8398>therewith<s%>: The world also is <S%H3559>established<s%>, that it cannot be <S%H4131>moved<s%>.
Thy <S%H3678>throne<s%> is <S%H3559>established<s%> of <S%H227>old<s%>: Thou art from <S%H5769>everlasting<s%>.

The <S%H5104>floods<s%> have lifted <S%H5375>up<s%>, O <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, The <S%H5104>floods<s%> have lifted <S%H5375>up<s%> their <S%H6963>voice<s%>; The <S%H5104>floods<s%> lift <S%H5375>up<s%> their <S%H1796>waves<s%>.

Above the <S%H6963>voices<s%> of <S%H7227>many<s%> <S%H4325>waters<s%>, The <S%H117>mighty<s%> <S%H4867>breakers<s%> of the <S%H3220>sea<s%>, <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> on <S%H4791>high<s%> is <S%H117>mighty<s%>.
